title = "Focused work"
description = "\"I like my quiet\", he says, nervously moving back and forth on his chair. 

\"I moved here some time ago, so I can fully concentrate on my work. Away from the people. Now I can spent time with my tools and listen to them work. 

Old Tom looks miserable. His body tells you he hasn't eaten anything for at least a week. With no food lying around, he is most likely to starve in here.

Without looking at you, he goes on talking: \"I'm busy with something big right now, but I can't tell you what it is.\"
